data.description: Large 4/2 home in great community with 2 car garage. Home needs minor cosmetic updating but overall great condition. Roof was replaced in 2021. Central AC original and in working condition. HOA is only $86 per month and covers cable, wifi, trash, fitness center, parks etc. Roof has solar panels that are leased and buyer will have to assume lease. Great property in family oriented neighborhood located near attractions and restaurants. Priced to sell. All offers to be accompanied by pof or pre-approval letter.
